overview.en: ANBI global digital trading platform was established and operated in the Republic of Seychelles, which focusing on the Transaction Fee Mining model.Users transaction can enjoy the return of the fee, if you hold ABB daily you also can enjoy the platform fee& high dividends.ANBI provides users ABB subsidy in order to guarantee our user benefits.
overview.zh: AnBi安币交易平台成立并运营于塞舌尔共和国，主打“交易挖矿”模式，ABB是安币平台的平台币。用户交易可享受手续费返还和持有ABB每日享受平台手续费高额分红；此外平台承诺以发行价对平台币ABB破发托底，保证平台用户利益。
